      <item>
        <title>Make Smite Single-Target</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Shrimpy]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Why should it make the Paladin conversion immune?  I want the success of Smite to be more reliant on the skill of the Paladin predicting who is going to get converted.  If the Paladin Smites somebody else and gets converted himself, it’s not like he hurt his new team.  So I don’t think he should be conversion immune while smiting.</p>
          <p><a href="https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/make-smite-single-target/53050/8">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
